SQL Query Basics

	=> Filtering Data

		WHERE
		AND / OR
		BETWEEN
		IN
		LIKE
		LIMIT

	=> Sorting Data

		ORDER BY
		ASC / DESC

	=> Aggregate Functions

			COUNT() - SELECT COUNT(*) FROM employees;
			SUM() - SELECT SUM(salary) FROM employees;
			AVG() - SELECT AVG(salary) FROM employees;
			MIN() - SELECT MIN(salary) FROM employees;
			MAX() - SELECT MAX(salary) FROM employees;

